'''七姊妹學院'''（{{lang-en|Seven Sisters}}）是形容[[美國東北部|美國東北部地區]]7所[[美國文理學院|文理學院]]间松散关系的一個称呼<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/536520/Seven-Sisters |title = Seven Sisters |publisher = Encyclopædia Britannica |language = en |quote = "...consortium of seven highly prestigious private institutions of higher education in the northeastern United States. At the time of the consortium’s inception, all of its members were women’s colleges." |accessdate = 2014-09-11 |archive-date = 2013-12-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131207215924/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/536520/Seven-Sisters |dead-url = no }}</ref>，因這些學院曾經都是[[美國女子文理學院|女子學院]]而得名。7所學院均成立于[[19世紀|19世紀]]，至今仍有5所學院延續這種教育傳統，而另外2所則出於多個因素不再僅允許女性讀[[本科|本科]]。

